  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain a bonus equal to 1 + 1 per 4 ranks you possess in the Craft (alchemy) skill on saving throws against any alchemical item you use or create. In addition, whenever you and an adjacent creature would both be affected by one of your alchemical items, you can forego the normal bonus granted by this ability and apply it as a penalty to the creature&#8217;s AC or saving throws against the item&#8217;s effects or attacks made with the item.</p>\n",
